{"tid":1786320,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[Excel達人/IT人入] 有無咩方法模擬 excel內置嘅inspection tool?","createTime":"2019-12-17T05:06:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T01:49:35.000Z","uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ca4d4f92fab1f49485720bfac4c3a293dc440d9a","tid":1786320,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T05:06:08.000Z","msg":"喺Excel 如果我地入錯啲formula 會提我地有error e.g. 除左0時會有bug report<br />\n咁假設我想整個excel表入一啲球員嘅入球數<br />\ne.g.<br />\nGoals by player, Messi<br />\nMatch A, 3<br />\nMatch B, 4<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n如果我唔小心入左個負數 或者入左隻字入去 可以彈個error俾我睇 (用任何方式)<br />\ne.g.<br />\nMatch D, -1 (err: incorrect goal number format)<br />\n<br />\n或者入左個好大嘅數會有warning<br />\ne.g.<br />\nMatch E, 100 (warning: unrealistically large goal number)<br />\n<br />\n有咩方法可以容易做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 喺excel入呢啲條件又怕有人改個excel時會郁左佢check嘅位置 例如做剪貼時會帶埋條formula走<br />\n或者有咩tools可以用?<br />\n只需要check ==,!=,&gt;,&lt;,or, and組成嘅condition<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://我上網搵到篇paper用.Net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%88%91%E4%B8%8A%E7%B6%B2%E6%90%B5%E5%88%B0%E7%AF%87paper%E7%94%A8.Net&d=oGSqBYpvdEZZERTBUGrA0qnpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=9eebf52a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">我上網搵到篇paper用.Net</a> C#寫 但有無現成/更易方法去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1901.11100\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Farxiv.org%2Fabs%2F1901.11100&d=oGSqBYpvdEZZERTBUGrA0qnpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=f88ef02e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/1901.11100</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2c568c62e87528658c3cd95246701bc4ba3a51e","tid":1786320,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T05:12:43.000Z","msg":"直接用資料驗證唔得?"},{"pid":"1f13b036e45be08bf02cd43a4f7237176fc45905","tid":1786320,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2c568c62e87528658c3cd95246701bc4ba3a51e","tid":1786320,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T05:12:43.000Z","msg":"直接用資料驗證唔得?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T05:36:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Thanks Check下夠唔夠用先 因為我其實想做幾個level 有複合嘅data e.g. Ronaldo7 球員+波衫number 如果可以用regex去check就更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f37bf077fed95833f09b27eb27482e8860afba3c","tid":1786320,"uid":25345,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T01:48:03.000Z","msg":"vba 入面有 selectionchange 或 change event<br />\n加幾句if就得,好簡單"},{"pid":"0ca03d296e99004fbd60f9ca4af460199fc3f0e5","tid":1786320,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f37bf077fed95833f09b27eb27482e8860afba3c","tid":1786320,"uid":25345,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T01:48:03.000Z","msg":"vba 入面有 selectionchange 或 change event<br />\n加幾句if就得,好簡單"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T11:03:06.000Z","msg":"睇一睇先 thanks巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b3104c033b7dd61ec2bb52d3dd5b9f16b1fb6d7","tid":1786320,"uid":130698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T01:49:35.000Z","msg":"Conditional formatting?"}]}